The feature that we must support in the first version (MVP)
1. Organizers can create activity
2. Users can join activity
3. Users can quit the activity before a specific time( set by the organizer, usually one day before the activity)
4. Users can mark himself as paid(need to choose by cash or by paypay)
5. Organizers can easily know who hasn't paid
6. When the joiners reached the capacity of the activity, the following joiners will become candidate, they need to wait the queue.
7. Waiters can be notified when he/she become formal joiners(in the case enough joiners quit the activity)
